<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٩٩ سورة الزلزلة]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>[سورة الزلزلة <span class="c2">(٩٩)</span> : الآيات ١ الى ٦]<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>إِذا زُلْزِلَتِ الْأَرْضُ زِلْزالَها <span class="c2">(١)</span> وَأَخْرَجَتِ الْأَرْضُ أَثْقالَها <span class="c2">(٢)</span> وَقالَ الْإِنْسانُ ما لَها <span class="c2">(٣)</span> يَوْمَئِذٍ تُحَدِّثُ أَخْبارَها <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>بِأَنَّ رَبَّكَ أَوْحى لَها <span class="c2">(٥)</span> يَوْمَئِذٍ يَصْدُرُ النَّاسُ أَشْتاتاً لِيُرَوْا أَعْمالَهُمْ <span class="c2">(٦)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١-<span class="c5"> إِذا زُلْزِلَتِ الْأَرْضُ زِلْزالَها:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>إِذا زُلْزِلَتِ الْأَرْضُ إذا حركت الأرض واضطربت.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>زِلْزالَها أقوى ما يكون التحريك والاضطراب.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٢-<span class="c5"> وَأَخْرَجَتِ الْأَرْضُ أَثْقالَها:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>أَثْقالَها ما فى بطنها.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>٣-<span class="c5"> وَقالَ الْإِنْسانُ ما لَها:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَقالَ الْإِنْسانُ فى دهشة وفزع.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>ما لَها ما للأرض تزلزلت وتخرج أثقالها.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>٤-<span class="c5"> يَوْمَئِذٍ تُحَدِّثُ أَخْبارَها:</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>تُحَدِّثُ تحدث الأرض الإنسان.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>أَخْبارَها التي أفزعته.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>٥-<span class="c5"> بِأَنَّ رَبَّكَ أَوْحى لَها:</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>أَوْحى لَها أن تزلزل وتضطرب.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>٦-<span class="c5"> يَوْمَئِذٍ يَصْدُرُ النَّاسُ أَشْتاتاً لِيُرَوْا أَعْمالَهُمْ:</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>يَصْدُرُ النَّاسُ من قبورهم سراعا.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>أَشْتاتاً متفرقين.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>